Somsak Chivavibul



Mr. Somsak Chivavibul is Chief Decision Management Officer & Executive VP at Navient Corp. Mr. Chivavibul was previously employed as Senior Vice President by SLM Corp., Treasurer by Student Loan Marketing Association, and Senior VP-Financial Planning & Analysis by Sallie Mae Bank. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Maryland.



