Somsak Chivavibul, Chief Financial Officer



Profile
Connections






Biography



    Somsak Chivavibul, Chief Financial Officer, Navient - April 2014 to present. Senior Vice President, Financial Planning & Analysis, SLM Corporation - May 2007 to April 2014. Vice President, Financial Planning & Analysis, SLM Corporation - 2003 to 2007. Treasurer, Student Loan Marketing Association - 1997 to 2003. Managing Director, Financial Planning & Analysis, SLM Corporation - 1997 to 2003. Chivavibul is appointed as the company's executive vice president and chief decision management officer on March 27, 2017.
    





Board Membership




Somsak Chivavibul is not a member of any boards




 


  







